          "segments": [
            "2. [2/65] al-Kafi: A number of our companions from Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Isa from Ali b. al-Nu’man from Ismail b. Jabir from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام who said: the book of Allāh – in it is an account of what came before you and a report of what will come after you and a judgment of what is between you (of differences) – and we do know it (all)."
          ],
          "text": "2. [2/65] al-Kafi: A number of our companions from Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Isa from Ali b. al-Nu’man from Ismail b. Jabir from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام who said: the book of Allāh – in it is an account of what came before you and a report of what will come after you and a judgment of what is between you (of differences) – and we do know it (all)."
